msgstr "Előfizetésed lemondásra került a számlázási időszak végén."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is switched from yearly to monthly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:60
msgid "Your subscription has been switched to monthly billing."
msgstr "Előfizetésed havi számlázásra váltott."

#. Toast success shown after a Plutonium subscription is switched from monthly to yearly billing.
#: src/features/app/components/dialogs/components/plutonium/hooks/useSubscriptionActions.ts:56
